{"id":689,"date":"2020-08-21T06:04:32","date_gmt":"2020-08-21T06:04:32","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/about\/"},"modified":"2023-02-10T07:43:42","modified_gmt":"2023-02-10T07:43:42","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/about\/","title":{"rendered":"About"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull\" style=\"min-height:456px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-0 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"826\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1560\" alt=\"\" src=\"http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/background-banner-scaled.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/background-banner-scaled.jpg 2560w, http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/background-banner-300x97.jpg 300w, http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/background-banner-1024x331.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/background-banner-768x248.jpg 768w, http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/background-banner-1536x496.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/background-banner-2048x661.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignfull are-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flex wp-container-4\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow\">\n<h1 class=\"has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color wp-block-heading\">About Me<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#ffffff\">During the last 7+ years as a design professional, I\u2019ve been working with dozens of companies from various industries, helping them to build new services and improve existing ones.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-2\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button has-custom-font-size is-style-outline has-medium-font-size\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color\" href=\"http:\/\/designermadhan.local\/my-resume\/\">My Resume<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:15px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>My core skills lie in the intersection of design and technology, which means that I\u2019m skilled in designing digital experiences with an iterative and data-driven approach, but I\u2019m also comfortable communicating with the development team to solve more technical problems.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>I enjoy working on projects that have a positive impact on the surrounding society and the environment, in addition to the business in question. On a team level, I strive to work with individuals who have different backgrounds, because I genuinely believe that diverse teams produce the best results.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"inherit-container-width wp-block-group alignfull has-ast-global-color-5-background-color has-background is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"ast-oembed-container\" style=\"height: 100%;\"><iframe title=\"Motion Graphics CV\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/pR9p1EnNDhk?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"inherit-container-width wp-block-group alignfull has-